Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你光芒普照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的照耀之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心灵一隅会生出阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法照亮你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1910)}玛利亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还真是个聪明的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从你身边逃走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个眼神是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却洞穿一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将不加修饰的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实收入眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不加修饰的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准… 看穿我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么毫不慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她… 她明明失去了大泽玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使故地重游 我还是没法杀死亡灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 还是没能做个了结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我一起上路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我 又会被留在列车里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连同思念 忏悔 后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又会像那天一样在此失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又将藕断丝连的留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不去追大泽玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而执着于我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南 我是个说到做到的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚的事 由我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你可不准死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不想受你保护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你并肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使看不到颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能感受到玛利亚的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以知道 是因为玛利亚是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你力量的泉源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你通过寻找新的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,企图摆脱夏姆的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚不是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友而战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那份剪不断 理还乱的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然凭那点心愿就解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许你走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在这里 由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这个手感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛在殴打白色的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要两个迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们拥有同一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 夏姆不会叫我阿尔法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他只在最后叫过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只为满足一己私欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自然会领悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新名字的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}孤独{\r}」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天就不会重演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就能摆脱夏姆的亡灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是现出奇怪的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时像夏姆的咖啡色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天更是纯白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆死后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的… 你的心也随他去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都成了我无可忘却的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有停滞在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定权在活人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为生者 我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许你再死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许你死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若在这里无法拯救什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那天还有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁 你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实被束缚在那个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我以为 只要造出迦南那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能接近… 接近夏姆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南早已被解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从夏姆的亡灵中 从不断重复的那一天中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有同一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有同样刺青的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏姆 你阴魂不散的纠缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要摆脱「{\1c&H0000FF}蛇{\r}」的诅咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中指挑这边 对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是呢 迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多事 要向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没法复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没法复原？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经没法回到过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤口比预想中的浅 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 这里不是天国？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这么死气沉沉的天国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和芸芸说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她拼命把你背来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大泽 芸芸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实先生 这里是极乐净土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先我们一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛 南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯 我还活着呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那快救救玛利亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后… 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给可怜的芸芸上点供品吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供品最好是馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭她恢复精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于迦南 我查了你手机拨过的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经停机了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起待了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果对迦南还是一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南眼中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南肩负的重担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看 想去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本以为终于可以和她并肩而立了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要体谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的愿望是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她想保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 还是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论走到何方 迦南都不让我和她并肩而立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能 你们的境遇差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们可以互相偎依吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相偎依？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 如果只让心相依的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只让心相依…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那座灰色的城市里 只有玛利亚闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不是我希望和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚就不会遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无论身在何方 我都能感受到玛利亚的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 无论身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕天各一方 我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,产蟹旺季仍遥遥无期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市和我们初履之时别无二致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有新闻略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已经没人感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}新生的空白接连被新的色彩所掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊 电话邮件都联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个奇怪事件怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「消失的村庄」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不要提了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有另一个猛料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么料？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上海 有个男人为某位女性倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苦恋未果 追寻着她的芳踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子低级小说啊 认真点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跳槽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这本低级小说的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我来书写
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(400,200)}♪还活着啊 因为因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 出门也不关电视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那小屁股多翘 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把芸芸的药给爸爸寄去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说能复制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了 她本人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工打得太多 来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 老兄 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好 差不多该进入下一首了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}致即将踏入新世界的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}送上奈奈的一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这曲子还真是应景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}敬请欣赏 来自听众「丝绸之路馒头」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「LIFE」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丝绸之路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馒头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充斥着喧嚣的洪流 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你过去不是拿「好厉害」当口头禅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想最近都没听到你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了站在迦南身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是感叹周围的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要让自己变厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家各自努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼搏着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实并不是无法企及的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能像实先生所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心心相依吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉 香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吃香蕉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油加香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要道别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准拿商品垫胸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让顾客高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这座城市的种种邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面凝聚着我对红尘的留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这座城市的所见所闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这座城市的纷纭思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命 如此绚烂夺目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人无法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 尽管眼睛生疼 我还是正视了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个普通女孩的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是死性不改 还敢用我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这句话原样奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何况这次对手特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独臂的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
